# MRE Project Analysis — Missing Code & Broken Joins Fix

## Problem Summary

After a full audit of all 12 crates in the workspace, I identified **major structural disconnects** between what crates expose/expect and what their dependents actually import. The code was generated with two separate "dialects" of the API that don't match — the **architecture doc dialect** (used by `sequencer`, `risk-engine`, `sim`) and a **different dialect** (used by `matching-engine`, `gateway`, `order-book/apply.rs`). These need to be reconciled into a single coherent API surface.

